Introduction

Park Rossi is a South Korean singer and dancer under LSA Entertainment. She was a temporary member and Dancer of the South Korean girl groups FlyWithMe and their dance sub-unit Flora under the stage name Ella under FA Entertainment and the Leader and Dancer of Another Level (formerly NEWRED) under the stage name Rossi under ROADLIGHT Entertainment.

On June 27, 2018, she debuted as a temporary member of FlyWithMe with the release of their first digital single, "Your Face". She left the group on December 31, 2020, and joined the girl group Another Level under the new stage name Rossi. Another Level disbanded unofficially between March 2021 and March 2022.

She later made her solo debut on February 20, 2023, with the single “Gossip“, under the new stage name Park Rossi.
